      <title>法国股市反弹乏力，债券因勒庞保证而保持稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/french-markets-stabilize-as-traders-digest-le-pen-assurances</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员们权衡极右翼领导人玛丽娜·勒庞 (Marine Le Pen) 是否保证如果她在全国大选中获胜，她将与总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙 (Emmanuel Macron) 合作，法国股市缩减涨幅，债券小幅波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/french-markets-stabilize-as-traders-digest-le-pen-assurances</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 09:03:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
